Here now, behold! upon my bended Knees, I confeſs the Juſtice of the Court, ask Mercy of this abus'd Corporation, and bid Adieu to it, and all my ſilly and credulous Votaries, in theſe mournful Words:



                        Good People, I own that our Riſe was unjuſt;



                        Our Fall, the Deſert of Deceit and of Luſt.
